<br>
Resistance is solely based on level difference and foe's resist (I think I've read somewhere that resist difference between you and the foe does affect it too.. I'm still not sure about this).<br>
<br>
As for poking the foes to add 50 damage... well poking an Ulthork would make 50 more damage on a 4k+ foes while a single of his three attackes per round makes 130+ damage on my poor 1khp. Do the math...<br>
